A driver has survived a horror smash after his car hurtled into a wall , flipped over and left him trapped under the weight of the vehicle .
His jeans were left on the underside of the red car after firefighters spent 25 minutes to free the man .
The man , believed to be in his 20s suffered head and chest injuries , but remained conscious during the efforts to cut him free .
Medics say he was fortunate to still be alive given the severity of the crash .